==English==
===Noun===
'''epicycloid''' (''plural'' '''epicycloids''')
{{wikipedia}}
#{{geometry}} The [[locus]] of a [[point]] on the [[circumference]] of a [[circle]] that [[roll]]s without [[slip]]ping on the circumference of another circle.

